{"tid":232011,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"放假係屋企煮咩好---芝士龍蝦伊麵+香濃南瓜湯","createTime":"2017-05-06T12:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T12:06:43.000Z","uid":97096,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b1e1c83632bc8e1979a6344e8931bed8f304c23","tid":232011,"uid":97096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:47:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n因為有人話我煮急凍海鮮唔好<br />\n所以今日就用新鮮海鮮煮大餐食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cR38vG5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcR38vG5.jpg&h=b14314b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o95Gh8y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo95Gh8y.jpg&h=9824894d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"399adb38659049b667b8679c09668c56f3a7d960","tid":232011,"uid":45848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f518bf8c950819bb61e4964c5c3899578242f584","tid":232011,"uid":97096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:56:32.000Z","msg":"首先係芝士龍蝦伊麵<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/205306_d27980482e079b5f00289b0f12623e71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F205306_d27980482e079b5f00289b0f12623e71.jpg&h=12288d9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n材料: <br />\n1. 龍蝦<br />\n2. 芝士<br />\n3. 伊麵<br />\n4.少少蒜茸<br />\n5. 少少黑椒<br />\n6. 鹽<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2389a0d0525abcd008e953b1e6cd6a759c816c13","tid":232011,"uid":4719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:01:10.000Z","msg":"隻匙羹好唔襯"},{"pid":"1e726362f92fb5cfb72ef851881e3c9b5b85a650","tid":232011,"uid":97096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/205736_659097c2f01b122515642060b9f49e20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F205736_659097c2f01b122515642060b9f49e20.jpg&h=3f1be5d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新鮮既龍蝦我係街市買的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我叫呀姐幫我劏埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到黎就只係剪咗d鬚同用水沖下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黑色個d係龍蝦膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係超多膏呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就撒d鹽同黑椒係上面就攞去蒸<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/210437_e49bfde41e0d7294f8b078ef8e57e756.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F210437_e49bfde41e0d7294f8b078ef8e57e756.jpg&h=500e778f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/210437_c656097897acf605d512f094b487a69f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F210437_c656097897acf605d512f094b487a69f.jpg&h=7998e95a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0c4f080a20169db49d556038d51c2e710c3c395","tid":232011,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:08:09.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0522495dca15b1402b45916c3dca1d5b5beef1e8","tid":232011,"uid":97096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:11:35.000Z","msg":"大約過咗10-15分鐘<br />\nD龍蝦就應該熟了<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/210704_45a1a6cb03dafee1f77e8a99cfde420a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F210704_45a1a6cb03dafee1f77e8a99cfde420a.jpg&h=3a7f7706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搬d龍蝦去個焗盤度先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/85Gsn6F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F85Gsn6F.jpg&h=89ab9c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蒸完有d汁係碟底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好浪費<br />\n用黎一陣燴伊麵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M1kQ6bx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM1kQ6bx.jpg&h=f12f1c42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e150d357b75e9b7d41958764b66333ca0fee6337","tid":232011,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:12:57.000Z","msg":"隻龍蝦貴唔貴"},{"pid":"a48c7047e914c3840e0dda1e489ee29af1039eb9","tid":232011,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:14:43.000Z","msg":"斷"},{"pid":"5eba9fa4d709caa2c47e9df4a0ef4dab3aa341de","tid":232011,"uid":97096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/211252_9f91c52799d56571749524efeb7530ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F211252_9f91c52799d56571749524efeb7530ba.jpg&h=7c38224c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伊麵買返黎一定要用水煮一煮先<br />\n因為好多油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/211531_d22e56c87ea933d316232168bc11d357.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F211531_d22e56c87ea933d316232168bc11d357.jpg&h=9accf18a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nD伊麵用水煮完之後就倒咗d水佢<br />\n然後落頭先d龍蝦汁燴d麵<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/211825_787896fd4cd12c00c7f8fed71d1baefd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F211825_787896fd4cd12c00c7f8fed71d1baefd.jpg&h=4b6501ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n收咗水就可以上碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a6ccb2f96c97521533dc65756a5efc483ba87d","tid":232011,"uid":97096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:19:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻龍蝦貴唔貴</blockquote><br />\n一隻138蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae92c5f0746d207ab88f5cde99d95262df8faa0c","tid":232011,"uid":97096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hr1dcOu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHr1dcOu.jpg&h=4d3ce750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伊麵得咗就可以整龍蝦<br />\n加埋芝士，蒜茸就可以放入焗爐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1g7jj5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1g7jj5M.jpg&h=d2d61a33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n200度焗3-5分鐘就得la<br />\n之後就放係d伊麵上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完成！"},{"pid":"0ff30b008bfe9ba2e2d8e18ea3c7fac095d3a270","tid":232011,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:23:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隻龍蝦貴唔貴</blockquote><br />\n一隻138蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似幾抵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e71ba01bee3f5e0ff39edae421f8d8c0c6f213","tid":232011,"uid":25969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"正到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ffb0ee178cc3f98bf9991e3df5c7890a93944f1","tid":232011,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"證明容器同食物既配合係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d748a4595788c6654188edb5640f9d6cf187af","tid":232011,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:27:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>隻龍蝦貴唔貴</blockquote><br />\n一隻138蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似幾抵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過食一次成本都要200蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n那有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca4982e2c1e858550c734e00fb3be4d9e2d4956","tid":232011,"uid":97096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1L37so7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1L37so7.jpg&h=371aa9ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9tbFxxW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9tbFxxW.jpg&h=21e1667b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVZ7y13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVZ7y13.jpg&h=515eff86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住就南瓜湯<br />\n材料:<br />\n1. 南瓜<br />\n2. 洋蔥<br />\n3. 甜椒<br />\n4. 紅蘿蔔<br />\n5. 茴香<br />\n6. 黑椒<br />\n7. 雞湯or 清水<br />\n8.鹽"},{"pid":"3295a513ed7e0f077f7abecbd2d1c7033ead7970","tid":232011,"uid":1345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:29:41.000Z","msg":"蒸完啲肉唔會散咩"},{"pid":"1804a2616e551211afe208f50c440911ddc1fc21","tid":232011,"uid":110719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:33:15.000Z","msg":"聚左你 去我屋企煮比我食 咁我就唔使學"},{"pid":"9984219c7cc902964b7b0bf090189253438f06bc","tid":232011,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:35:40.000Z","msg":"芝士邊度買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee06c375597913a9866aeb2d4d0a58271ab3ddb","tid":232011,"uid":97096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMrpT77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMrpT77.jpg&h=66c97ba9&s={SIZE}\" />將所有野洗乾淨，切碎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/213020_69fdfbf59d8737d5aac4debf72d4ed37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F213020_69fdfbf59d8737d5aac4debf72d4ed37.jpg&h=369dd696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先炒咗d南瓜<br />\n南瓜開始熟就落洋蔥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3XyB955.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3XyB955.jpg&h=db2a5b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洋蔥都炒到香個時就落埋其他菜<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/213537_2d06e737b4e42eb0f8c98c3965969ab3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F213537_2d06e737b4e42eb0f8c98c3965969ab3.jpg&h=b766f3e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4yXX2cS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4yXX2cS.jpg&h=f0ee02c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n炒到所有野都熟，就可以加雞湯入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/213859_aff6575d2f8ea9061aee87c9725daf22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F213859_aff6575d2f8ea9061aee87c9725daf22.jpg&h=160bc12f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煮到滾就可以熄火，放涼少少"},{"pid":"d230a3e624acd73879a0110e583147badac6cd34","tid":232011,"uid":97096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:42:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蒸完啲肉唔會散咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會呀"},{"pid":"640a4993c21ea817ed0f4f123a5bd41753a1bf1d","tid":232011,"uid":97096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>芝士邊度買<img sr